ld]]\n| ''[[King Charles III (play)|King Charles III]]''\n|-\n| [[Jonathan Kent (director)|Jonathan Kent]]\n| ''[[Long Day's Journey into Night]]''\n|-\n| [[Joe Mantello]]\n| ''[[The Humans (play)|The Humans]]''\n|-\n| [[Liesl Tommy]]\n| ''[[Eclipsed (play)|Eclipsed]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\"| '''2017'''<br>{{small|[[71st Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| [[Rebecca Taichman]]\n| ''[[Indecent (play)|Indecent]]''\n|-\n| [[Sam Gold]]\n| ''[[A Doll's House, Part 2]]''\n|-\n| [[Ruben Santiago-Hudson]]\n| ''[[Jitney (play)|Jitney]]''\n|-\n| [[Bartlett Sher]]\n| ''[[Oslo (play)|Oslo]]''\n|-\n| [[Daniel J. Sullivan]]\n| ''[[The Little Foxes]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\"| '''2018'''<br>{{small|[[72nd Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| [[John Tiffany]]\n| ''[[Harry Potter and the Cursed Child]]''\n|-\n| [[Marianne Elliott (director)|Marianne Elliott]]\n| ''[[Angels in America]]''\n|-\n| [[Joe Mantello]]\n| ''[[Three Tall Women]]''\n|-\n| [[Patrick Marber]]\n| ''[[Travesties]]''\n|-\n| [[George C. Wolfe]]\n| ''[[The Iceman Cometh]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" align=\"center\"| '''2019'''<br>{{small|[[73rd Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| [[Sam Mendes]]\n| ''[[The Ferryman (play)|The Ferryman]]''\n|-\n| [[Rupert Goold]]\n| ''[[Ink (play)|Ink]]''\n|-\n| [[Ivo van Hove]]\n| ''[[Network (play)|Network]]''\n|-\n| [[Bartlett Sher]]\n| ''[[To Kill a Mockingbird (2018 play)|To Kill a Mockingbird]]''\n|-\n| [[George C. Wolfe]]\n| ''[[Gary: A Sequel to Titus Andronicus]]''\n|}\n\n==Award records==\n===Multiple wins===\n; 6 Wins\n* [[Mike Nichols]]\n\n; 3 Wins\n* [[Jerry Zaks]]\n\n; 2 Wins\n* [[Peter Brook]]\n* [[John Dexter]]\n* [[Marianne Elliott (director)|Marianne Elliott]]\n* [[Gerald Gutierrez]]\n* [[Peter Hall (director)|Peter Hall]]\n* [[Jack O'Brien (director)|Jack O'Brien]]\n* [[Gene Saks]]\n\n===Multiple nominations===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n; 10 Nominations\n* [[Mike Nichols]]\n\n; 8 Nomination