y Boys]]''\n|-\n| [[Wilson Milam]]\n| ''[[The Lieutenant of Inishmore]]''\n|-\n| [[Bartlett Sher]]\n| ''[[Awake and Sing!]]''\n|-\n| [[Daniel J. Sullivan]]\n| ''[[Rabbit Hole]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" align=\"center\"| '''2007'''<br>{{small|[[61st Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| [[Jack O'Brien (director)|Jack O'Brien]]\n| ''[[The Coast of Utopia]]''\n|-\n| [[Michael Grandage]]\n| ''[[Frost/Nixon (play)|Frost/Nixon]]''\n|-\n| David Grindley\n| ''[[Journey's End]]''\n|-\n| [[Melly Still]]\n| ''[[Coram Boy (play)|Coram Boy]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" align=\"center\"| '''2008'''<br>{{small|[[62nd Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| [[Anna D. Shapiro]]\n| ''[[August: Osage County]]''\n|-\n| [[Maria Aitken]]\n| ''[[The 39 Steps (play)|The 39 Steps]]''\n|-\n| [[Conor McPherson]]\n| ''[[The Seafarer (play)|The Seafarer]]''\n|-\n| [[Matthew Warchus]]\n| ''[[Boeing Boeing (play)|Boeing Boeing]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" align=\"center\"| '''2009'''<br>{{small|[[63rd Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| [[Matthew Warchus]]\n| ''[[God of Carnage]]''\n|-\n| [[Phyllida Lloyd]]\n| ''[[Mary Stuart (play)|Mary Stuart]]''\n|-\n| [[Bartlett Sher]]\n| ''[[Joe Turner's Come and Gone]]''\n|-\n| [[Matthew Warchus]]\n| ''[[The Norman Conquests]]''\n|}\n\n===2010s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:98%;\"\n|- style=\"background:#bebebe;\"\n! style=\"width:11%;\"| Year\n! style=\"width:35%;\"| Director\n! style=\"width:54%;\"| Production\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" align=\"center\"| '''2010'''<br>{{small|[[64th Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| [[Michael Grandage]]\n| ''[[Red (play)|Red]]''\n|-\n| Sheryl Kaller\n| ''[[Next Fall (play)|Next Fall]]''\n|-\n| [[Kenny Leon]]\n| ''[[Fences (play)|Fences]]''\n|-\n| [[Gregory Mosher]]\n| ''[[A View from the Bridge]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" align=\"center\"| '''2011'''<br>{{small|[[65th Tony Awards]]}}\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n| [[Marianne Elliott (director)|Marianne Elliott]] and 